-- UBS Aims to Take on Riskier Investments, CEO Tells Die Welt
-- B y   C o r n e l i u s   R a h n
-- 2010-10-30T10:54:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-30/ubs-aims-to-take-on-riskier-investments-ceo-tells-die-welt.html
UBS AG aims to take more risks in
its investment-banking unit to increase profitability,  Welt am
Sonntag  reported, citing Chief Executive Officer  Oswald Gruebel .  The risks currently taken are too low when compared with
rival Deutsche Bank AG, Gruebel was cited as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
